# 8. BEST PRACTICE RECOMMENDATIONS

## Keep Story Data Static Initially

Recommended:

* JSON file
  OR
* Pre-seeded database records

Avoid:

* Dynamic story editor
* AI-generated story logic

---

## Keep Game Logic in Service Layer

Correct:

```plaintext id="50j2vd"
Controller -> Service -> Repository
```

Wrong:

```plaintext id="r7i1p4"
Controller contains all game logic
```

---

# 9. RECOMMENDED DESIGN PATTERNS FOR MVP

Only use patterns that provide real value.

| Pattern  | Use                    |
| -------- | ---------------------- |
| Builder  | Create scenes          |
| Strategy | Handle choice outcomes |
| Factory  | Generate events        |

Avoid excessive patterns for academic MVP.

---

# 10. FINAL MVP DEFINITION

A successful MVP means:

✅ User creates profile
✅ User reads story scenes
✅ User makes choices
✅ Choices affect outcome
✅ Health changes properly
✅ User can lose or win
✅ Progress saves properly
✅ Game is playable from start to finish